---
// Slide 5: Workflow Program (7 Steps)
---

<div class="slide-frame inactive w-full" id="slide-5" data-slide="4">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <span class="text-sm font-bold text-neonLime uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">
        05 // Operational Workflow
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-outfit text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
        Workflow Program
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Horizontal Grid Timeline -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-4 pt-4">
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 space-y-2 hover-lift glow-lime">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-neonLime font-mono">STEP 01</span>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">
          Industry Brief
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Saygon memberikan tantangan &amp; studi kasus nyata.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 space-y-2 hover-lift">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 font-mono">STEP 02</span>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">
          Research &amp; Ide
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Proses eksplorasi, riset pasar &amp; ide kreatif oleh siswa.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 space-y-2 hover-lift">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 font-mono">STEP 03</span>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">
          Production
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Tahap produksi aset di sekolah menggunakan lab studio.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 space-y-2 hover-lift">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 font-mono">STEP 04</span>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">
          Quality Review
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Guru bertindak sebagai Creative Director menguji standar.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 space-y-2 hover-lift glow-indigo">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-neonIndigo font-mono">STEP 05</span>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">
          Pitching Session
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Siswa mempresentasikan hasil kreasi di depan tim Saygon.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 space-y-2 hover-lift">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 font-mono">STEP 06</span>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">
          Bidding / Select
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Kurasi karya terbaik dipilih langsung oleh industri.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 space-y-2 hover-lift glow-lime">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-neonLime font-mono">STEP 07</span>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">
          Revision &amp; Out
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Penyempurnaan aset final yang siap didistribusikan.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-4 flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-slate-500 font-mono border-t border-white/5">
      <span>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-nodes text-neonLime mr-2"></i>Professional Standard
      </span>
      <span>
        Seluruh alur merefleksikan alur kerja industri kreatif profesional
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
